for the Amazing Racer

[1] Directional Light
Reduced the amount of light to make use of a flashlight.
[2] Fog
Made a red fog to give it an apocolyptic atmosphere.
[3] Skybox
Sun is bigger, atmosphere is thicker, and the sky tint is orange.
[4] Player
Given a "latern" to be able to light up their surroundings. I also made them jump a little lower to make some areas more challenging.
[5] Finish Zone
Made 3 finish zones: one green(the main), one blue, and one red (to purposely blend in)
For the particle effects, I added have a color over lifetime, size over lifetime, a trail, and some noise to it to give it a sort of "random" effect.
[6] Terrain
Made the terrain have 3 paths: a linear path(the main), a hidden one, and a hidden one in the hidden one (hidden-ception)
